name: David Milwain's Drum Book
description:
David Milwains Drum Book is an instructional guide to playing the drums. It includes many of the different units that will be covered throughout your time as a drum student. It includes a wide variety of exercises, increasing in level of difficulty, to help you improve your skill behind the drum set. 

This book utilizes many patterns, rhythms and exercises that, if used correctly, will expand your knowledge and know-how behind the drum set. Using and excelling at these patterns, rhythms and exercises will help you to creatively branch out with new ideas to develop your own style and rock the drums!

• 130+ pages with 19 individual sections.
• Over 450 unique drumming patterns and exercises.
• A glossary containing many important drumming terms.
